	use \&.

2024-11-19  Bruno Haible  <bruno@clisp.org>

	doc: Use GNU coding style in man pages.
	Reported by Ð½Ð°Ð± <nabijaczleweli@nabijaczleweli.xyz> in
	<https://lists.gnu.org/archive/html/bug-gettext/2022-01/msg00019.html>.

