2018-11-05  Bruno Haible  <bruno@clisp.org>

	xgettext: Add support for C11 string literals.
	* gettext-tools/src/x-c.c (phase5_get): Recognize the u8"..." syntax.
	* gettext-tools/tests/xgettext-c-25: New file.
